name: 04 Memory Card - Costa de Silver Jaw
description: The motto "always get the job done" is a thing he always holds. That is the reason why he became one of Ziggy's right hands (the black market dealer). Having a sturdy and large body, a face decorated with silver jaws, and cold-handed, he becomes a quite fearful debt collector. He is not a person who likes small talk and any form of 'rejection' about work.
